  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "ch35-01",
      "text": "C'est l'enfance d'Avril.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the warm Franklin family laboratory in 1931, little Avril sits on the floor facing the viewer, playing with brass gears, while her parents work at a nearby bench. A wall calendar clearly shows 1931. The scattered brass gears in Avril's small hands are the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Golden oil lamp light fills the cozy room, innocent and nostalgic mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "childhood",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch35-02",
      "text": "Avril a peur.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "childhood",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch35-03",
      "text": "L'enfance est belle car Avril a son papa et sa maman.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "childhood",
      "speaker": "Pops"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch35-04",
      "text": "Avril a peur parce que le monde va mal.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "childhood",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch35-05",
      "text": "Pops regarde Avril.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "childhood",
      "speaker": "Pops"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch35-06",
      "text": "L'avenir est dans le labo.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the 1931 Franklin laboratory, the family gathers around a glowing experiment facing the viewer, young Avril perched on her father's shoulders pointing forward. The bright glow of the experimental device on the workbench is the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Warm gaslight mingles with the experiment's glow, hopeful and forward-looking mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "future",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch35-07",
      "text": "On vise l'avenir.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "future",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch35-08",
      "text": "L'avenir est bon.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "future",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch35-09",
      "text": "Avril vise le monde.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "future",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch35-10",
      "text": "On pense à l'avenir.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "future",
      "speaker": "Pops"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch35-11",
      "text": "Il y a 2 semaines.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the 1931 laboratory, the Franklin family works together at the bench facing the viewer, a wall calendar behind them showing two weeks crossed off in red ink. The marked calendar with its crossed-off days is the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Soft daylight through a window mixes with oil lamp glow, bittersweet and fleeting mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "two_weeks",
      "speaker": "Pops"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch35-12",
      "text": "On se lève le jour.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "two_weeks",
      "speaker": "Pops"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch35-13",
      "text": "La semaine passe.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "two_weeks",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
